/***************************************
 ****** Goodix Driver Description ******
 **************************************/
1. File Contents

├── gh_common.c
├── gh_common.h
├── gh_platform.c
├── gh_bus_access.c
├── gh_customer.c
├── gh_customer.h
└── Makefile

2. Description

gh_common.c        The main file of drivers, register spi/i2c, device node, file operations.

gh_platform.c      Specific the hardware control of fingerprint module.

gh_bus_access.c    Specific the SPI/I2C communication method of fingerprint module.

gh_customer.c      Specific the power current and voltage.

3. How to build *.ko out of kernel source directory

make ARCH=arm64 CROSS_COMPILE=<path_to_your_toolchain> KDIR=<kernel source dir>

